		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> <date>Sept. 6. 1845</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">My Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Your two letters are now before me&#44; and I<lb/> have particularly noted the contents&#59;&#8212;with respect to the<lb/> subscribers to the Occident&#44; I will endeavor to collect the<lb/> subscriptions as soon as possible &#38; remit you the amount&#58;<lb/> with respect to the Institute which we are endeavoring to<lb/> establish here&#44; I am afraid it will come to nothing&#44; for<lb/> our Brethren here as you correctly state are indeed &#39;rude and<lb/> uneducated&#44;&#39; and are also tainted with infidelity&#44; bigotry<lb/> and superstition&#59;&#8212;We have a constantly <sic>encreasing</sic> Jewish<lb/> population&#44; nearly numbering 3&#44;500 but they are not of the right<lb/> sort&#44; a moiety<add>&#63;</add> of them being more willing to receive assistance<lb/> than to assist or lend their support to either of the two<lb/> Congregations&#59; <del>or</del> for educational purposes&#59;&#8212;but at the same time must give them credit for being Charitable&#59; for calls<lb/> of that nature are indeed numerous&#59; as a specimen&#44; upwards<lb/> of &#36;500 was collected from them &#38; the societies for the suffering at the <placeName><sic>Pitsburg</sic></placeName> fire&#59;&#8212;when your <add>Hebrew</add> is <sic>compleated</sic> it is probable<lb/> I may be able to dispose of a few&#44; if you think proper to send<lb/> them out&#59;&#8212;The Occident does not appear to the taste of our members&#44;<lb/> a work of the plan of the &#8220;Voice of Jacob&#44;&#8221; or the &#8220;Jewish Chronicle&#8221;<lb/> would suit much better&#44; <sic>their</sic> are several subscribers to those<lb/> works&#44; &#38; they appear to take very much&#44; controversial works<lb/> in favor of our Religion are required very much in the <placeName>West</placeName>&#44;<lb/> I am a considerable portion of my time&#44; answering different<lb/> text of Scriptures&#44; for Clergymen in various sections of the <placeName>Western<lb/> Country</placeName>&#59; brought me by our Israelitish Pedlar&#59; a cheap pub&#45;<lb/>&#45;lication of that nature would be very beneficial&#59; as</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>constant struggles are made to obtain converts amongst<lb/> our Brethren&#59;&#8212;and those Pedlars &#39;tho honest moral men&#44; are in<lb/> general composed of very illiterate Germans&#44; who are not able<lb/> to give an answer to the plainest text&#59;&#8212;Your Occident is<lb/> calculated for the <hi rend="underline">Rich</hi> and <hi rend="underline">educated Jew</hi>&#44; <hi rend="underline">not for</hi> the poor<lb/> and illiterate Sons of <placeName>Israel</placeName>&#44; who only know that they are Jews.<lb/> they want something to warm them up as patriots in a</p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>118 South 4th Street. Philadelphia</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(center)indent(2)"><placeName>Pa</placeName></p>
				<p rend="Note&#58;">The address is written sideways in the center of the page.</p>
				<p>national point of view&#44; as well as to stir up their zeal<lb/> in our holy Religion&#59;&#8212;we are not as in <placeName>Europe</placeName> writing with<lb/> this word of Persecution at our throats&#59;&#8212;being on an equality with<lb/> the Gentile&#44; we are required to be strong &#38; courageous&#59; and altho&#39; few<lb/> in numbers against the Midianitish<add>&#63;</add> Camp&#44; to sound our &#39;Trumpets&#39;<lb/> break our &#39;Pitches&#44;&#39; and <hi rend="underline">Proclaim aloud</hi> &#8220;The Sword of the Lord<lb/> and of <persName>Gideon</persName>.&#8221;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Yours Sincerely</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName role="author">Joseph Jones<add>&#63;</add></persName></p>
		</body>
